## Annex II — Technical and organisational measures (Art. 32 GDPR)

The technical and organisational measures to be implemented by the data importer
are documented in the attached TOM: **`tom_{{ run_id[:8] }}.md`**

Minimum standards per protection goal (Art. 32(1)(b) GDPR):

- **Confidentiality:** encryption at rest and in transit (AES-256, TLS 1.2+), role-based access control
- **Integrity:** signatures/checksums, documented authorisations
- **Availability:** backup concept, contingency plan
- **Resilience:** redundancy, deputisation arrangements
- **Recoverability:** tested recovery procedure
- **Pseudonymisation:** where technically feasible, prior to transfer
- **Auditability:** audit logging, regular review

